# Inky MCP Server

This package provides an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for accessing your personalized Inky coding rules through MCP-compatible clients like Cursor, Windsurf, and Claude Desktop.

## Features

- Search your coding rules using semantic similarity
- Retrieve specific rules by ID
- List all your rules
- Secure token-based authentication

## Usage

The server communicates with the Inky backend API using your personal access token. Get your token from the Inky dashboard and add it to your MCP configuration.

